data.description: PRICE REDUCED. SELLER MOTIVATED! Beautiful well maintained 3 bed, 2 bath single-family home nestled in the Gramercy Farms Community, St. Cloud. The home is like new and has very nice features such as ceiling fans, screened porch, vinyl wood type , gutters, water softener, blinds, solar panels and sprinklers. This gem has no front or rear neighbors and comes with fantastic community amenities such as playground, basketball court, dog park and picnic area making it the perfect place to call home! This beautiful home is your gateway to a life of comfort, tranquility, and community camaraderie. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a vibrant and welcoming neighborhood with everything you need at your doorstep. The community is short drive from Lake Nona Area, St Cloud Downtown, Florida Turnpike and US 192. Don't lose the opportunity and schedule your showing today.
